OL,3,CTory donor apologises for reportedly
OL,4,Csaying Diane Abbott 'should be shot'
OL,6,FThe Conservative party's biggest donor
OL,7,Fhas said he is "deeply sorry" after
OL,8,Freportedly saying former Labour MP
OL,9,FDiane Abbott made him "want to hate
OL,10,Fall black women" and that "she should
OL,11,Fbe shot".
OL,13,FFrank Hester, chief executive of The
OL,14,FPhoenix Partnership (TPP), has
OL,15,Fadmitted making "rude" comments, which
OL,16,Fwere first reported by , but said they
OL,17,Fhad "nothing to do with her gender nor
OL,18,Fcolour of skin".
