OL,6,FLabour and the Liberal Democrats are
OL,7,Fcalling on the Tories to return the
OL,8,Fmoney Mr Hester has donated to the
OL,9,Fparty.
OL,11,FMr Hester donated #10 million to the
OL,12,FTories last year, according to
OL,13,FElectoral Commission records.
OL,15,FHe individually donated #5 million to
OL,16,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak's party in
OL,17,FMay and gave another #5 million via
OL,18,Fhis healthcare software firm in
OL,19,FNovember.
