OL,6,FThe Guardian reported that Mr Hester's
OL,7,Fremarks about Ms Abbott were made in
OL,8,F2019, meaning that they likely
OL,9,Foccurred when she was shadow home
OL,10,Fsecretary under former Labour leader
OL,11,FJeremy Corbyn.
OL,13,FThe newspaper reported that during a
OL,14,Fmeeting at his Leeds company
OL,15,Fheadquarters, Mr Hester, having
OL,16,Fpreviously criticised an executive at
OL,17,Fanother organisation, went on to
OL,18,Fdiscuss Ms Abbott, the first black
OL,19,Fwoman elected to parliament.
