OL,6,FHe reportedly said: "It's like trying
OL,7,Fnot to be racist but you see Diane
OL,8,FAbbott on the TV, and you're just
OL,9,Flike... you just want to hate all
OL,10,Fblack women because she's there.
OL,12,F"And I don't hate all black women at
OL,13,Fall, but I think she should be shot.
OL,14,F(The executive) and Diane Abbott need
OL,15,Fto be shot."
