OL,3,CTory donor apologises for reportedly
OL,4,Csaying Diane Abbott 'should be shot'
OL,6,FIn a statement released via his firm,
OL,7,FMr Hester said he had rung Ms Abbott
OL,8,Fon Monday to "apologise directly for
OL,9,Fthe hurt he has caused her".
OL,11,FThe statement said: "Frank Hester
OL,12,Faccepts that he was rude about Diane
OL,13,FAbbot in a private meeting several
OL,14,Fyears ago but his criticism had
OL,15,Fnothing to do with her gender nor
OL,16,Fcolour of skin.
OL,18,F"The Guardian is right when it quotes
OL,19,FFrank saying he abhors racism, not
OL,20,Fleast because he experienced it as the
OL,21,Fchild of Irish immigrants in the 1970s.
