OL,6,F"He rang Diane Abbott twice today to
OL,7,Ftry to apologise directly for the hurt
OL,8,Fhe has caused her, and is deeply sorry
OL,9,Ffor his remarks.
OL,11,F"He wishes to make it clear that he
OL,12,Fregards racism as a poison which has
OL,13,Fno place in public life."
OL,15,FBut Tory opponents have seized on the
OL,16,Fremarks and urged the governing party
OL,17,Fto give back the cash Mr Hester and
OL,18,Fhis company have donated.
