OL,6,FMs Abbott, first elected as MP for
OL,7,FHackney North and Stoke Newington in
OL,8,F1987, has sat as an independent since
OL,9,FApril after the Labour whip was
OL,10,Fwithdrawn following comments she made
OL,11,Fin The Observer suggesting Jewish,
OL,12,FIrish and Traveller people are not
OL,13,Fsubject to racism "all their lives".
OL,15,FShe is awaiting the outcome of an
OL,16,Findependent complaints process set-up
OL,17,Fby Labour to investigate her remarks.
